room_title: Escape room "Abducted" by Escape Game Erie in Erie
room_description: A bit dazed and confused, you stir back to consciousness. The last thing you remember is walking to your car after an enjoyable dinner with friends. Now you find yourself blindfolded and bound at the wrist. Work with your fellow abductees to find clues, solve puzzles, decipher codes, and anything else required to outwit your captor and escape the room before your time runs out.
